      "totalCount": 540,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=935955&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1442&rangeEnd=1469",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/62b329c05e481362b0ed9cb?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1442&rangeEnd=1469"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "935955_3_1783-1842",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1783-1842",
      "markText": "在此我能想到的这些相对的弱势群体的日常武器有：偷懒、装糊涂、开小差、假装顺从、偷盗、装傻卖呆、诽谤、纵火、暗中破坏等等",
      "totalCount": 518,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=935955&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1783&rangeEnd=1842",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/62b329c05e481362b0ed9cb?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1783&rangeEnd=1842"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "935955_4_579-658",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "579-658",
      "markText": "每一种矛盾都既是价值的冲突，也是利益的冲突；每一种“需求”在它成为“应然”的过程中，都含有情感和“要求”（反之亦然）；每一种阶级斗争同时也是关于价值观的斗争。",
      "totalCount": 414,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=935955&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=579&rangeEnd=658",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/62b329c05e481362b0ed9cb?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=579&rangeEnd=658"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "935955_3_1582-1647",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1582-1647",
      "markText": "无论是哪种革命的成功——我并不想否认这些成果——通常都会导致一个更大的更具强制力的国家机器，它比其前任更有效地压榨农民以养肥自己。",
      "totalCount": 351,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=935955&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1582&rangeEnd=1647",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/62b329c05e481362b0ed9cb?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1582&rangeEnd=1647"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "935955_3_662-712",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "662-712",
      "markText": "绝对以国家利益为中心的历史记录和档案鼓励了这种迷恋，它们从不提及农民，除非农民的行动对国家构成威胁。",
      "totalCount": 300,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=935955&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=662&rangeEnd=712",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/62b329c05e481362b0ed9cb?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=662&rangeEnd=712"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "935955_7_5322-5695",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "5322-5695",
      "markText": "这给人以遵从的印象，却没有实质内容。但是象征秩序，即司机的通行权，并未遭到直接挑战；实际上，行人表面上表现出的匆忙便是对象征秩序的认可和巩固。几乎可以认为，将象征遵从最大化恰是为了使实际遵从最小化。",
      "totalCount": 294,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=935955&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=5322&rangeEnd=5695",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/62b329c05e481362b0ed9cb?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=5322&rangeEnd=5695"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "935955_9_9476-9559",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "9476-9559",
      "markText": "我让他们（年轻人）记住：你们是在出卖劳动力，而买它的人要看到他能从中有所收益，所以当他在旁边时就干，他一走开就歇，但是记住当监视者在场时你们一定要看上去是一直在工作。",
      "totalCount": 288,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=935955&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=9476&rangeEnd=9559",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/62b329c05e481362b0ed9cb?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=9476&rangeEnd=9559"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "935955_3_972-1019",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "972-1019",
      "markText": "贯穿于大部分历史过程的大多数从属阶级极少能从事公开的、有组织的政治行动，那对他们来说过于奢侈。",
      "totalCount": 272,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=935955&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=972&rangeEnd=1019",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/62b329c05e481362b0ed9cb?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=972&rangeEnd=1019"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "935955_3_4345-4387",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "4345-4387",
      "markText": "我发现需要保持一种审慎的中立——亦即保持缄默，这是明智的，但同时也是巨大的心理负担。",
      "totalCount": 270,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=935955&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=4345&rangeEnd=4387",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/62b329c05e481362b0ed9cb?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=4345&rangeEnd=4387"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "935955_5_1958-2008",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1958-2008",
      "markText": "拉扎克是村里的“贫困户”，他的房子不仅仅对他而言是一种尴尬，对大多数塞达卡人来说也是一种集体的耻辱。",
      "totalCount": 225,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=935955&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1958&rangeEnd=2008",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/62b329c05e481362b0ed9cb?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1958&rangeEnd=2008"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "935955_6_2140-2177",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "2140-2177",
      "markText": "他生活的方方面面都充斥着克己精神，只有一方面除外：他允许自己娶了三个老婆。",
      "totalCount": 225,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=935955&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2140&rangeEnd=2177",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/62b329c05e481362b0ed9cb?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2140&rangeEnd=2177"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "935955_5_13671-13743",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "13671-13743",
      "markText": "如果我们因为他们偷窃而不给他们救济，他们也许会一直偷窃下去。”这是我听到的最清楚地认识到为了对穷人进行社会控制而对其进行慈善施舍的重要性的言论。",
      "totalCount": 209,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=935955&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=13671&rangeEnd=13743",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/62b329c05e481362b0ed9cb?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=13671&rangeEnd=13743"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "935955_5_12944-12977",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "12944-12977",
      "markText": "而他声誉上的额外成本却是最小的，他的地位实际上已经确定在最低点了。",
      "totalCount": 180,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=935955&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=12944&rangeEnd=12977",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/62b329c05e481362b0ed9cb?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=12944&rangeEnd=12977"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "935955_7_3828-3918",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "3828-3918",
      "markText": "这是一种讽刺：一方面，只有违背对人慷慨和体谅他人的原则，他们才能获得土地、收入和权力；另一方面，只有遵守对人慷慨和体谅他人的原则，他们才能获得好名声。现在，他们实际上不受制裁约束。",
